onth treasury bill (T-Bill) following the House's ratification on UU on state bonds (SUN). The T-Bill is intended to refinance bonds maturing in 2003 and in the following years, official said. \par \par \uc2  "For the time being we would not issue the one month or three month T-Bill, but the six month and a year one," Director General of Financial Institution at the Ministry of Finance Darmin Nasution said yesterday after a plenary meeting with the \b \highlight22\uc2 House of Representatives\b0 \highlight\uc2 . \par \par \uc2  T-Bill is bond issued by government and sold in the competitive bidding. In US, it is a core instrument of monetary \b \highlight22\uc2 policy\b0 \highlight\uc2  of Federal Reserve Bank. \par \par \uc2  Darmin added the T-Bill issuance is a combination of reprofiling \b \highlight22\uc2 policy\b0 \highlight\uc2  government made last week including assets to bond swap by IBRA. But he was still \b \highlight22\uc2 uncertain\b0 \highlight\uc2  about the number and amount of the to be issued T-Bill as his office was still unprepared of the infrastructure as well as auction \b \highlight22\uc2 regulation\b0 \highlight\uc2 . Besides BI would also have to prepare the \b \highlight22\uc2 regulation\b0 \highlight\uc2  for the central industry sector. \par \par \uc2  Minister of Finance added SUN is a \b \highlight22\uc2 fiscal\b0 \highlight\uc2  instrument used to finance the state \b \highlight22\uc2 budget\b0 \highlight\uc2 . It also is an instrument of \b \highlight22\uc2 public\b0 \highlight\uc2  investment sold in the capital market abroad. \par \par \uc2  "SUN is one of the financing sources of the state \b \highlight22\uc2 budget\b0 \highlight\uc2 ." \par \par \uc2  Boediono expected the UU SUN would encourage people to give contribution to the state \b \highlight22\uc2 budget\b0 \highlight\uc2  by transferring their savings to SUN. \par \par \uc2  The plenary meeting, which was presided by Vice House Speaker Tosari Wijaya was considerably of a